Root Cause Fixed:
Previous toggle button was child element inside #console-panel div. When console.style.display='none' was set, entire panel including button became invisible. User could not click invisible button to restore console visibility. External button is now separate DOM element outside console panel, remaining visible at all times.

Pattern Followed:
- CLAUDE.md global window export pattern (window.toggleConsole)
- Inline onclick handler pattern (onclick="window.toggleConsole()")
- Drag handle external DOM pattern (separate element appended to body)
- Private field encapsulation (#externalToggleBtn)

